# 05. Figure 3A

Figure 2D is a set of PWM sequence logos for seven CREB/ATF-family transcription factors.

This plot uses Table S2 PWM/PSSM values only:

```text
~/cre_repro/data/1-s2.0-S2589004223028249-mmc3.xlsx
```

It does not use MPRA expression data and does not require transcpp fitting.

## Preparation

Export the Excel sheet first:

```bash
python /path/to/repo/common/export_tables.py
```

If the exported PWM CSV has a Korean sheet-name filename, copy or rename it to:

```text
~/cre_repro/work/csv/pwms.csv
```

Example:

```bash
cp ~/cre_repro/work/csv/pwms__시트1.csv ~/cre_repro/work/csv/pwms.csv
```

## Plot

```bash
python plot_fig2d_sequence_logos.py
```

## Method

The supplementary Table S2 values are treated as base-2 log-odds PSSM values. With equal background base frequency:

```text
weight(base) = 0.25 * 2^(PSSM score)
P(base) = weight(base) / sum(weights at that position)
entropy = -sum(P(base) * log2(P(base)))
information = 2 - entropy
letter height = P(base) * information
```

Colors:

```text
A green
C blue
G orange
T red
```

TF order:

```text
CREB1, CREB3, CREB5, CREM, ATF1, ATF4, ATF7
```

Note: The CREB3 logo produced from the supplement matched the downloaded CIS-BP/Jolma M03042 motif, while the paper figure visually appeared closer to another CREB3 motif variant. This difference affects the visual CREB3 logo but not the model XML that used the supplementary PWM values.

